            setCookie(cookieName, true);              redirect(toRedirectURL);          }       }()) /*]]&gt;*/ &lt;/script&gt; </code></pre>  <p>Now, what should i do, to open the redirecting site2nd without giving me the pop blocked option in browser.</p>  <p><strong>OR</strong></p>  <p>Give me <strong>another script</strong>, which work to redirect site1st to site2nd to open in new tab. </p>